<D>__{yeah.}
<A>__{thelma starts to dig through her bag again.}
<C>__{thelma}
<D>__{it's in here somewhere.}
<A>__{louise is rubbing her face. she looks pretty bad. her hands are shaking.}
<C>__{louise}
<D>__{shit. i'm gettin' tired.}
<C>__{thelma}
<D>__{are you alright?}
<A>__{louise does not really seem alright.}
