<D>__{nobody would believe us. we'd still get in trouble. we'd still have our lives ruined. and you know what else?}
<C>__{louise}
<D>__{what?}
<C>__{thelma}
<D>__{that guy was hurtin' me. and if you hadn't come out when you did, he'd a hurt me a lot worse. and probably nothin' woulda happened to him. 'cause everybody did see me dancin' with him all night. and they woulda made out like i asked for it. and my life woulda been ruined a whole lot worse than it is now. at least now i'm havin' fun. and i'm not sorry the son of a bitch is dead. i'm only sorry that it was you that did it and not me. and if i haven't, i wanna take this time to thank you, louise. thank you for savin' my ass.}
